{"tid":2434566,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣男入郵局拒掃安心出行 打傷職員被捕","createTime":"2021-03-05T15:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T16:52:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4168e0123ee82f223a0ba8ccaf6ad4581d25d66","tid":2434566,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"荃灣郵政局在今早（5日）約9時發生傷人案，一名姓李的58歲男子，在進入位於荃灣西樓角路38號政府合署1樓的荃灣郵政局時，懷疑因未有使用「安心出行」掃碼，以及未有登記個人資料，在被郵局職員查問時突然情緒激動，然後發難並用手襲擊職員。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場後，經初步調查，將案件列作普通襲擊並拘捕該名男子，現時交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進。郵局職員手部受傷，其後被送往仁濟醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，該名被捕男子操不純正廣東話口音，今晨進入郵局時拒絕登記安心出行，繼而毁壞公物，職員阻止他離開時，該名男子突然發狂，襲擊職員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210305/W6LZ4QF3MJA7RCJFCOIDGMTG2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210305%2FW6LZ4QF3MJA7RCJFCOIDGMTG2Q%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedWCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=0791e039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210305%2FW6LZ4QF3MJA7RCJFCOIDGMTG2Q%2F&h=102e1d67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210305/W6LZ4QF3MJA7RCJFCOIDGMTG2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"765eb204c206b793dd36519154c6523a81b14f6d","tid":2434566,"uid":168169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:33:25.000Z","msg":"抵打 操你媽嗰B"},{"pid":"79e923cce7628e5ed34351c3eb3d0f4cd7e57a61","tid":2434566,"uid":7323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">痛快，抵打</span>"},{"pid":"91f0380e8474a4f19f31612da7efac84f5ce64d2","tid":2434566,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"手足respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2e4f8b4b65b8f7d8e653047e0ebfebe6898323","tid":2434566,"uid":40723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"有幾分似蛋餅強"}